ygData.subject: Tynkale's quest
ygData.msgSnippet: I had heard about that drunkard one, but I talked with him and he said I had to bring back the hide of some monster called the jojunga in the Innothule Swamp
ygData.messageBody:
I had heard about that drunkard one, but I talked with him and he said I had
to bring back the hide of some monster called the jojunga in the Innothule
Swamp being that is on a whole other continent and right next to the Trolls
(Hate to run into their Bashers on the perimeter) I would think this quest
would give something of value. Well I am going to the other continent soon so
who knows what is ahead.

Sha'kel
